Name: Average time from 'Declaration SUBMITTED by EMPLOYEE' to 'Request Payment'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Declaration SUBMITTED by EMPLOYEE' and activity 'Request Payment'

Name: Average time from 'Declaration FINAL_APPROVED by SUPERVISOR' to 'Request Payment'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Declaration FINAL_APPROVED by SUPERVISOR' and activity 'Request Payment'

Name: Average time from 'Request Payment' to 'Payment Handled'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Request Payment' and activity 'Payment Handled'

Name: Total time from 'Declaration SUBMITTED by EMPLOYEE' to 'Request Payment' for cases rejected by 'Declaration REJECTED by PRE_APPROVER' before approval
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Declaration SUBMITTED by EMPLOYEE' and activity 'Request Payment'

Name: Total time from 'Declaration APPROVED by ADMINISTRATION' to 'Request Payment'
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Declaration APPROVED by ADMINISTRATION' and activity 'Request Payment'

Name: Average resolution time of 'Request Payment'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity Request Payment and the end of the case

Name: Minimum time from 'Declaration APPROVED by BUDGET OWNER' to 'Request Payment'
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity 'Declaration APPROVED by BUDGET OWNER' and activity 'Request Payment'

Name: Total resolution time of 'Request Payment' in cases with 'Declaration REJECTED by PRE_APPROVER'

Name: Average time from 'Declaration REJECTED by PRE_APPROVER' to 'Request Payment' in subsequent submissions
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Declaration REJECTED by PRE_APPROVER' and activity 'Request Payment'

Name: Total time for 'Request Payment' in processes involving 'Declaration APPROVED by PRE_APPROVER'
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Request Payment' and the end of case where activity 'Declaration APPROVED by PRE_APPROVER occurs

Name: Average waiting time to 'Request Payment' after 'Declaration APPROVED by ADMINISTRATION'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Declaration APPROVED by ADMINISTRATION' and activity 'Request Payment'

Name: Minimum resolution time of 'Request Payment' in cases without 'Declaration REJECTED by PRE_APPROVER'
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity Request Payment and the end of the case

Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Declaration REJECTED by EMPLOYEE' and activity 'Request Payment'
